# Generated protobuf stubs are NOT committed. CI (the "Generate and Validate
# Code" job) regenerates and compiles them for every language, and the release
# workflow regenerates and publishes them to each registry. Only the canonical
# .proto source and hand-written package scaffolding live in the repo.
*.pb.go
*_pb2.py
*_pb2.pyi
*_pb2_grpc.py
*.pb.cc
*.pb.h
packages/proto-java/src/main/java/
packages/proto-kotlin/src/main/kotlin/
packages/proto-csharp/*.cs

